<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Dec 2024 01:13:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>科里卡预示着奥克兰的反应，澳超联赛新人出局</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/corica-heralds-auckland-response-a-league-newcomers-pull-clear-2024-12-29/</link><description>奥克兰足球俱乐部主教练史蒂夫·科里卡赞扬了球队应对澳超联赛首场失利的能力，新晋球队以 4-1 击败冠军中央海岸水手队，领先积分榜榜首 4 分。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Dec 2024 00:51:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/corica-heralds-auckland-response-a-league-newcomers-pull-clear-2024-12-29/</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称2025年是核问题的“重要一年”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-says-2025-important-year-nuclear-issue-2024-12-28/</link><description>伊朗周六表示，2025年将是其核问题的重要一年，准备迎接即将上任的美国总统唐纳德·特朗普可能重新实施“极限施压”政策。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 15:59:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-says-2025-important-year-nuclear-issue-2024-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国降低部分再生铜铝原材料进口关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cut-import-tariffs-some-recycled-copper-aluminium-raw-materials-2024-12-28/</link><description>中国政府周六表示，中国将从明年起降低乙烷和某些再生铜和铝原材料的进口关税。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 03:39:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cut-import-tariffs-some-recycled-copper-aluminium-raw-materials-2024-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普要求最高法院暂停可能禁止 TikTok 的法律</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/trump-asks-supreme-court-pause-law-that-could-ban-tiktok-2024-12-27/</link><description>当选总统唐纳德·特朗普敦促美国最高法院暂停实施一项禁止流行社交媒体应用 TikTok 或强制出售其的法律，称他上任后应该有时间对该问题寻求“政治解决”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 22:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/trump-asks-supreme-court-pause-law-that-could-ban-tiktok-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪巴西工厂的工人在“奴役般的条件下”接下来会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/what-happens-next-workers-slavery-like-conditions-byds-site-brazil-2024-12-27/</link><description>官员们与比亚迪和锦江集团就保护工人的进一步措施进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 21:53:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/what-happens-next-workers-slavery-like-conditions-byds-site-brazil-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：巴西在贩运指控后取消了中国比亚迪的临时工作签证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazilian-suspends-temporary-work-visas-byd-ministry-2024-12-27/</link><description>巴西外交部周五表示，在中国电动汽车生产商比亚迪旗下工厂的部分工人被指控成为人口贩运受害者后，巴西已停止向该公司发放临时工作签证。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 21:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazilian-suspends-temporary-work-visas-byd-ministry-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰泽连斯基：朝鲜人在战场上遭受损失，且没有俄罗斯军队的保护</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-north-koreans-suffering-battlefield-losses-unprotected-by-2024-12-27/</link><description>乌克兰总统泽连斯基周五表示，部署在俄罗斯库尔斯克地区的朝鲜军队遭受重大损失，并且得不到与他们并肩作战的俄罗斯军队的保护。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 20:36:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-north-koreans-suffering-battlefield-losses-unprotected-by-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国将第九家电信公司列入遭受中国支持的“盐台风”网络间谍活动攻击的公司名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-adds-9th-telcom-list-companies-hacked-by-chinese-backed-salt-typhoon-2024-12-27/</link><description>白宫高级官员周五表示，美国官员已将第九家电信公司添加到受到与中国有关的大规模网络间谍活动“盐台风”攻击的实体名单中。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 19:44:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-adds-9th-telcom-list-companies-hacked-by-chinese-backed-salt-typhoon-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，中国珠海撞车事件司机被判处死刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/driver-chinas-zhuhai-car-ramming-attack-sentenced-death-xinhua-reports-2024-12-27/</link><description>据中国官方新华社周五报道，中国南方珠海市驾车冲撞人群、造成至少 35 人死亡的司机已被判处死刑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 12:51:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/driver-chinas-zhuhai-car-ramming-attack-sentenced-death-xinhua-reports-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯法院称 TikTok 因违法行为被罚款 300 万卢布</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/russia-fines-tiktok-3-million-roubles-over-legal-violations-court-says-2024-12-27/</link><description>莫斯科法院新闻处称，俄罗斯法院周五对 TikTok 处以 300 万卢布（合 28,929.60 美元）罚款，原因是该公司未能遵守俄罗斯对传播某些信息的法律限制。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 12:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/russia-fines-tiktok-3-million-roubles-over-legal-violations-court-says-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>蒙古与法国欧安诺公司达成价值16亿美元的铀矿交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/mongolia-retracts-announcement-uranium-project-deal-with-frances-orano-2024-12-27/</link><description>蒙古周五表示，已与法国欧拉诺矿业集团达成初步协议，开发一个期待已久的价值16亿美元的铀矿开采项目。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 10:58:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/mongolia-retracts-announcement-uranium-project-deal-with-frances-orano-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，中国在南海黄岩岛周围进行巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-conducted-patrols-around-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-12-27/</link><description>据中央电视台报道，中国海警周五在南海黄岩岛周围进行巡逻，以维护中国的领土权利。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 09:40:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-conducted-patrols-around-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国因美国向台湾出售武器而制裁军事公司和高管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-sanctions-military-firms-executives-over-us-arms-sales-taiwan-2024-12-27/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，中国已对七家军工企业及相关高管实施制裁，原因是美国向台湾提供武器援助和军售。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 08:58:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-sanctions-military-firms-executives-over-us-arms-sales-taiwan-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>雷巴基纳带领哈萨克斯坦队在联合杯首秀中击败西班牙队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/rybakina-takes-kazakhstan-past-spain-united-cup-debut-2024-12-27/</link><description>埃琳娜·雷巴基娜 (Elena Rybakina) 带领哈萨克斯坦队周五在珀斯 RAC 竞技场举行的联合杯首秀中以 2-1 战胜西班牙队，而高新宇则在中国队战胜巴西队的比赛中击败了比阿特丽斯·哈达德·马亚 (Beatriz Haddad Maia)。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 08:43:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/rybakina-takes-kazakhstan-past-spain-united-cup-debut-2024-12-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着人口老龄化，中国延长了卡车、公共汽车司机的驾照年龄限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-extends-license-age-limit-truck-bus-drivers-population-ages-2024-12-27/</link><description>作为应对人口老龄化、出生率下降和劳动力减少带来的挑战的更广泛努力的一部分，中国将扩大中型和大型公共汽车以及卡车司机的驾驶执照年龄限制。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 08:40:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-extends-license-age-limit-truck-bus-drivers-population-ages-2024-12-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>